A federal high court sitting in Ilorin, kwara state has affirmed Senator Rafiu Ibrahim as PDP senatorial Candidate for Kwara south district election. Justice Babagana Ashigar in his ruling directed the Independent National Electoral Commission to recognize Rafiu Ibrahim and include his name as a contestant. INEC had recognized the kwara state governor Abdulfatah Ahmed as the candidate while the governor had insisted on resigning as the candidate. 